The goal is to enhance personalization, efficiency, and service delivery for its 1.5 million customers nationwide. Insignia Financial is one of Australia's largest wealth management companies and owner of MLC Australia. Google Cloud is the new way to the cloud, providing AI capabilities across many of its offerings, including its MLC superannuation member experience platforms. The company expects the migration to significantly reduce complexity and manual effort associated with maintaining critical applications, while strengthening cybersecurity and compliance. Tighter integration with its BigQuery data lake is also expected to drive benefits, supporting Insignedia Financial's readiness for AI adoption at scale.
